Ooops, but it is useful for one thing: virtue signalling.

snippet.textDisplay:
You should mention that no one wants to be walking around w/ a gold, red or blue bandana around their face. iWork for a nationwide grocery franchise. We are personally allowed to wear masks WE supply. However I must say... people coming into a store should have the decency to wear a legit breathing mask or a scarf at the most. Wearing a skull faced biker rag & coming in w/ a few other older teens can be a bit too much! I’m already worried about everything I must do on top of wondering if our store will be held up.
Stay Alert,
Stay Healthy
Stay Loved!💜💜💜
